author: AP
title: Shelby Harris counting his blessings, not his lost millions
description: Denver Broncos defensive end Shelby Harris was expecting to command upwards of $9 million annually in free agency
content:
AURORA, Colo. (AP) — Shelby Harris is counting his blessings and not his lost millions.
“I’m just happy to have a job. There are millions of Americans who have lost their jobs because of this,” the sixth-year defensive tackle said of the coronavirus pandemic… [+3785 chars]
